A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Reverend Reginald B. Newman on the occasion of his
2 retirement; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Reverend Reginald B. Newman has demonstrated his commitment to teaching
4 the Gospel, witnessing Christ through word and deed, and addressing the physical,
5 psychological, intellectual, and spiritual needs of others; and
6 WHEREAS, since 1992, he has served as the Senior Pastor of Fountain of Faith Missionary
7 Baptist Church in Riverdale, Georgia; and
8 WHEREAS, his vision and direction have helped Fountain of Faith Missionary Baptist
9 Church grow in size and influence, uplifting the community like the light of Bethlehem and
10 serving as a spiritual leader and place for fellowship; and
11 WHEREAS, he was instrumental in the development of the Patrina T. and Reginald B.
12 Newman scholarship, that was established in 2009 to assist graduating high school seniors
13 in pursing secondary education opportunities; and
